ActAn Act to give effect to the Anishinsbek Nation Governance Agreement, to amend the Sechelt Indian Band Self-Government Act and the Yukon First Nations Self-Government Act and to make related and consequential amendments to other Acts
SubjectOrder Fixing October 1, 2022 as the Day on Which Part 1 of the Act, Other than Section 6, Comes into Force
PrecisORDER FIXING OCTOBER 1, 2022 AS THE DAY ON WHICH PART 1 OF THE ACT, OTHER THAN SECTION 6, COMES INTO FORCE in order to provide for the establishment and operations of a central Anishinabek Nation government and the local governments of the five First Nations.
